cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.MM 

The paper deals with image classification tasks and proposes a new augmentation strategy that improves the performance of convolutional neural networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the regularization effect of the proposed strategy, which is related to machine learning (cs.LG - Machine Learning) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI - Artificial Intelligence). The paper also mentions the use of the trained model for image captioning (cs.CL - Computation and Language) and detection tasks (cs.MM - Multimedia).
